	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aliquanto nunc melius quam hactenus habeo, licet apostema palati plene nondum subsederit; spero tamen brevi integram sanitatem per domini gratiam mihi fore restituendam; sed fiat voluntas eius!</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid memoratu dignum acceperis de comitiis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l108" cert="high">Davosianis</placeName>, gratificaberis mihi, si consignatum miseris.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8057" cert="high">Campellum</persName> nostrum cuperem succedere in locum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20473" cert="high">Ganthneri</persName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu, quod tuum fuerit, facias/cies<note type="margin">a.R.: corrig.!</note>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orandus est dominus, ut ipse faciat.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta <persName ref="p8057" cert="high">Campellum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas ad <placeName type="citizen_name">Kampum</placeName> literas per filium misi ad <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name">Lucium</persName>; spero illum eas curasse recte.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi scripta mea, quae remisisti, et quoniam dicis te ea descripsisse, relegi nunc, quae cum mitterem, tumultuarie consignaram, et deprehendi me per festinantiam praeteriisse caput illius 4; proinde, si placet, adiicie.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So dann die sprüch des allten testamentz nüt probierend, so werffe man hin das gantze nüwe testament, in welchem Christus und die apostlen all ir sachen probierend mitt dem allten Testament, und das ist ein rächter töuffischer artickel etc.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nullas a diebus iam 14 literas ab amicis accepi nisi unas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Bienna</placeName> vel <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Byela</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit eius ecclesiae minister famam apud eos sparsam in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> mortuam esse regis matrem et nescio quem principem, id quod non credes/o, donec certiora audiero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Apud nos per dei gratiam pacata sunt omnia.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Vigilandum vero erit contra lupum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20222">Borrhomeum</persName></foreign>, und sol man den Pündtern ynbillden, das er den Pündten wenig guͦts willens tragen könne, dorumb das sy imm siner muͦter bruͦder, den herren von Müß, vertriben; dan die zwen bruͤdern, Müß und <persName type="citizen_name">bapst Pius</persName> (der mitt sins bruͦders, Müssers, gällt zum bapst worden), habend zwo schwestern gehept; die ein ist vermächlet dem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20222">Borromey</persName> zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Meyland</placeName>, daher der cardinal wolff, die ander dem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7462" cert="high">Wolff Dietrychen von Hohenemps</persName>, von welcher harkummend der cardinal bischoff zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l257" cert="high">Constantz</placeName>, graff <persName type="citizen_name">Hanibal</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dise all hat ir vetter, der bapst, zuͦ cardinälen und graven gemachet, die sunst noch ein wyl unden an der stägen alls einspännig edellüth gestanden werend.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Jetzt sind sy erhöcht <foreign xml:lang="la">et cogitant vindictam.</foreign></s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Darumb luͦge man für sich.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec obiter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta d. d. consules, <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontisellam</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770">Carolum</persName>, <persName ref="p8186" cert="high">Bonettum</persName> et alios nostros amicos.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">4. novembris 1570.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An herren <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Thobiam Egli</persName>, pfarreren zuͦ S. Martin zuͦ <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>, minem lieben herren und bruͦder.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
